      "content": [
        {
          "type": "heading",
          "attrs": {
            "level": 1,
            "textAlign": "left"
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "Principles for writing error messages",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "attrs": {
            "textAlign": "left"
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "Thoughtful error handling enhances the usefulness of Teradata’s products and plays a crucial role in building trust with the users. It can also reduce support resources.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "attrs": {
            "textAlign": "left"
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "These principles are meant to help you design useful messages that embody Teradata’s voice as a trustworthy, knowledgeable, and proactive guide in the products.  ",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "attrs": {
            "textAlign": "left"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "horizontalRule"
        },
        {
          "type": "heading",
          "attrs": {
            "level": 2,
            "textAlign": "left"
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "Avoid showing a message",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "attrs": {
            "textAlign": "left"
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "The best error message is no error happening at all. The message and the error itself are disruptive to a user’s experience. They stand in the way between the user and their job to be done. Make sure the system can address errors on the back end to avoid showing an error message.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "attrs": {
            "textAlign": "left"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "horizontalRule"
        },
        {
          "type": "heading",
          "attrs": {
            "level": 2,
            "textAlign": "left"
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "Consider the message before the design components",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "attrs": {
            "textAlign": "left"
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "Most of Teradata’s existing error messages don’t have the right content. If we have to display an error message, first write out what the content needs to say and think through how you’re going to say it and in which order you’ll place the words.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "image",
          "attrs": {
            "alt": null,
            "src": "https://knapsack.imgix.net/site/covalent/cd-components-x3xzd0jdmpng",
            "title": null
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "attrs": {
            "textAlign": "left"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "heading",
          "attrs": {
            "level": 3,
            "textAlign": "left"
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "Anatomy of an error message",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "attrs": {
            "textAlign": "left"
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "Not every error message you design will look like this, but many will. Regardless of the cause or type of the error, the most useful error message includes 3 distinct parts in this order:",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "bulletList",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "attrs": {
                    "textAlign": "left"
                  },
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "What happened",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "attrs": {
                    "textAlign": "left"
                  },
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "The underlying cause (show only if helpful to the user)",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "attrs": {
                    "textAlign": "left"
                  },
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "How to fix it",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
